Use can define a class to be used as a macro:
  Input: "{@use javax0.jamal.builtins.Define as defidufi}{@defidufi z=13}{z}"
  Output: "13"

Use can define an alias for an already defined macro:
  Input: "{@use define as defidufi}{@defidufi z=13}{z}"
  Output: "13"

Use can define an alias for an already defined macro even when it is the escape macro:
  Input: "{@use escape as e}{@e`wuff` {{{{ }}`wuff`}"
  Output: " {{{{ }}"

